OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK council to introduce Lord's
OL,4,CPrayer and national anthem at meetings
OL,6,FReform UK's "flagship" council has
OL,7,Fvoted through changes to introduce the
OL,8,FLord's Prayer and national anthem at
OL,9,Fmeetings for "patriotism and
OL,10,Fheritage", while opposition branded
OL,11,Fthe move "performative politics".
OL,13,FMembers at Kent County Council have
OL,14,Fapproved updates to its constitution
OL,15,Ffollowing majority votes at its annual
OL,16,Fcouncil meeting on Thursday.
OL,18,FIt will mean that county council
OL,19,Fmeetings will start with the recital
OL,20,Fof the Lord's Prayer and end with
OL,21,Fsinging of the national anthem.
OL,26,@nD@MOUnD@VO]qD@NOUrD@IO]sD@JOUsD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
