OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK council to introduce Lord's
OL,4,CPrayer and national anthem at meetings
OL,6,FPutting forward the move, Reform UK's
OL,7,FChristopher Hespe said: "We are a
OL,8,FChristian monarchy, and this is about
OL,9,Fstandards, it's about patriotism, it's
OL,10,Fabout heritage, and it's about our
OL,11,Froots.
OL,13,F"It's about grounding us and accepting
OL,14,Fthat we have duties and
OL,15,Fresponsibilities."
OL,17,FCouncil officers have also been
OL,18,Fprompted to make sure the approved
OL,19,Frecommendations can be introduced in a
OL,20,Flawful way.
OL,26,@oD@YOUuD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
