PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK council to introduce Lord's
OL,4,CPrayer and national anthem at meetings
OL,6,FLabour group leader Alister Brady
OL,7,Fopposed the motion, telling
OL,8,Fcouncillors that he has been contacted
OL,9,Fby residents on the change, many who
OL,10,Fare "religious and all patriotic".
OL,12,F"They told me they see this as
OL,13,Fperformative politics, and this
OL,14,Fproposal should be seen as an
OL,15,Fembarrassment, the council should be
OL,16,Fgetting on with their jobs," he said.
OL,18,FLiberal Democrat member Mike Sole said
OL,19,Fthat patriotism is important, but "is
OL,20,Fnot a karaoke requirement".
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@aO]tD@AOUxD@\O]{D@cOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK council to introduce Lord's
OL,4,CPrayer and national anthem at meetings
OL,6,F"You can support Britain, support our
OL,7,Finstitutions, and support the monarchy
OL,8,Fwithout insisting that council
OL,9,Fmeetings conclude like last night at
OL,10,Fthe Proms," he added.
OL,12,FInstead he said the council should
OL,13,Funite around service such as fixing
OL,14,Froads and supporting vulnerable people
OL,15,Fas "patriotism in action".
OL,17,FMeanwhile some opposition members,
OL,18,Fsuch as Restore Britain's Oliver
OL,19,FBradshaw, said he supported the motion
OL,20,Fin principle "with a very clear word
OL,21,Fof caution".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]wD@DOUwD@YO]|D@NOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
