OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK council to introduce Lord's
OL,4,CPrayer and national anthem at meetings
OL,6,F"I do not want my religion turned into
OL,7,Fyour prop," he said.
OL,9,F"Let us ensure this is a genuine act
OL,10,Fof respect for faith, not as a piece
OL,11,Fof political theatre and posturing."
OL,13,FReform councillor Pamela Williams also
OL,14,Fsupported the "longstanding
OL,15,Ftraditions" and said nobody is
OL,16,Fcompelled to join in.
OL,18,FShe added: "Many residents that I have
OL,19,Fspoken with do value these moments and
OL,20,Fsee them as part of the character and
OL,21,Fdignity of public life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@KO]qD@AOUsD@dO]vD@OOUwD@KO]zD@
OL,26,ALOU}D@XO]
