PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779466274
OL,3,CReform UK council to introduce Lord's
OL,4,CPrayer and national anthem at meetings
OL,6,FBut leader of the opposition, Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat Antony Hook questioned: "What
OL,8,Fare you so afraid of trying to cut the
OL,9,Ftime for the opposition to speak?"
OL,11,FRestore Britain's group deputy leader
OL,12,FMaxine Fothergill also said she did
OL,13,Fnot believe cutting opposition
OL,14,Fspeaking time while expanding
OL,15,Fceremonial additions "sends the right
OL,16,Fmessage".
OL,26,@oD@bOUqD@bO]wD@VOUxD@HO]
